REAPER LD Plugin Set — steelblue studios
========================================

The MIT license in LICENSE covers the steelblue studios code only: the four
plugins, the installer, and the shared modules.

The two REAPER extensions shipped under extensions/ are NOT ours. They are
included unmodified, under their own licenses, so the plugins work without a
separate download:

  ReaImGui         LGPL-3.0-or-later   extensions/LICENSE-ReaImGui-LGPL-3.0.txt
  js_ReaScriptAPI  MIT                 extensions/LICENSE-js_ReaScriptAPI-MIT.txt

See extensions/NOTICE.txt for versions, authors, and where the source lives.
